          "name": "Barre de réassurance Wynstor",
          "desc": "Trust bar horizontale avec icônes SVG sprite",
          "html": "<aside class=\"overflow-auto bg-white shadow-sm rounded-3 ws-p ws-my\" aria-label=\"Engagements Wynstor\">\n  <div class=\"d-inline-flex flex-nowrap justify-content-start align-items-center gap-4\">\n    <div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\">\n      <span class=\"d-inline-flex ws-ico-bg-lg bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-4\">\n        <svg class=\"ws-ico\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"/svg/_sprite-wynstor.svg#package\"></use></svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"fw-medium small\">400+ références</span>\n    </div>\n    <hr class=\"vr mx-2 my-auto\" style=\"min-height:3rem;opacity:.1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\">\n      <span class=\"d-inline-flex ws-ico-bg-lg bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-4\">\n        <svg class=\"ws-ico\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"/svg/_sprite-wynstor.svg#shield-check\"></use></svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"fw-medium small\">Qualité garantie</span>\n    </div>\n    <hr class=\"vr mx-2 my-auto\" style=\"min-height:3rem;opacity:.1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\">\n      <span class=\"d-inline-flex ws-ico-bg-lg bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-4\">\n        <svg class=\"ws-ico\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"/svg/_sprite-wynstor.svg#truck\"></use></svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"fw-medium small\">Livraison sous 48h</span>\n    </div>\n    <hr class=\"vr mx-2 my-auto\" style=\"min-height:3rem;opacity:.1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\">\n      <span class=\"d-inline-flex ws-ico-bg-lg bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-4\">\n        <svg class=\"ws-ico\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"/svg/_sprite-wynstor.svg#handshake\"></use></svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"fw-medium small\">Devis pro sous 24h</span>\n    </div>\n    <hr class=\"vr mx-2 my-auto\" style=\"min-height:3rem;opacity:.1\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"d-inline-flex align-items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0\">\n      <span class=\"d-inline-flex ws-ico-bg-lg bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-4\">\n        <svg class=\"ws-ico\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"/svg/_sprite-wynstor.svg#headset\"></use></svg>\n      </span>\n      <span class=\"fw-medium small\">Conseil expert</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</aside>"
        },
        {
          "id": "trust-banner-cta",
          "name": "Bannière CTA devis",
          "desc": "Fond dégradé Wynstor, texte + bouton devis",
          "html": "<aside class=\"rounded-3 ws-p ws-my ws-bg-gradient\" aria-label=\"Demande de devis\">\n  <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between flex-wrap gap-3\">\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"ws-bloc-title\" style=\"font-size:2rem;color:#fff\">Besoin d'un devis pour votre établissement\u00a0?</div>\n      <p class=\"mb-0 ws-text-sm\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75)\">Réponse sous 24h, livraison sur site, facturation administrative.</p>\n    </div>\n    <a href=\"/devis\" class=\"btn btn-light fw-semibold ws-p\" style=\"border-radius:8px\">Demander un devis</a>\n  </div>\n</aside>"
        },
        {
          "id": "trust-marques",
          "name": "Bandeau logos marques",
          "desc": "Logos marques en ligne — drag depuis la galerie média pour remplacer les images",
          "html": "<div class=\"ws-bg-light rounded-3 ws-p ws-my text-center\">\n  <div class=\"ws-text-xs text-uppercase\" style=\"letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:1.6rem\">Nos marques partenaires</div>\n  <div class=\"ws-logos\">\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"Marque 1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"Marque 2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"Marque 3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"Marque 4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n    <img src=\"\" alt=\"Marque 5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n  </div>\n</div>"
        }
