          "desc": "3 colonnes, pastille numérotée + titre + texte",
          "html": "<div class=\"row g-4 ws-my\">\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div class=\"ws-bg-light rounded-3 ws-p h-100\">\n      <div class=\"ws-badge-num mb-3\" style=\"background:var(--bs-primary)\">1</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-bloc-title\">Premier avantage</div>\n      <p class=\"ws-text-sm mb-0\">Description courte. Chiffre concret si possible.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div class=\"ws-bg-light rounded-3 ws-p h-100\">\n      <div class=\"ws-badge-num mb-3\" style=\"background:var(--bs-success)\">2</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-bloc-title\">Deuxième avantage</div>\n      <p class=\"ws-text-sm mb-0\">Description courte. Un fait vérifiable.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div class=\"ws-bg-light rounded-3 ws-p h-100\">\n      <div class=\"ws-badge-num mb-3\" style=\"background:var(--ws-orange-500)\">3</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-bloc-title\">Troisième avantage</div>\n      <p class=\"ws-text-sm mb-0\">Description courte. Pas de superlatif, des faits.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
        },
        {
          "id": "grid-4-stats",
          "name": "Bande 4 chiffres clés",
          "desc": "4 stats en ligne, fond sombre",
          "html": "<div class=\"ws-bg-dark rounded-3 ws-p ws-my\">\n  <div class=\"row g-4 text-center\">\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div class=\"ws-stat-number\" style=\"color:var(--bs-primary)\">20+</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-text-xs\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:0.4rem\">années d'expertise</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div class=\"ws-stat-number\" style=\"color:var(--bs-success)\">48h</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-text-xs\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:0.4rem\">livraison standard</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div class=\"ws-stat-number\" style=\"color:var(--bs-warning)\">24h</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-text-xs\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:0.4rem\">devis personnalisé</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"col-6 col-md-3\">\n      <div class=\"ws-stat-number\" style=\"color:var(--ws-orange-400)\">200€</div>\n      <div class=\"ws-text-xs\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);margin-top:0.4rem\">livraison offerte dès</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
        },
